  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/90eb5cff90fa620362b1be73fce44c76.avif?t=1748182179\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras_big/90eb5cff90fa620362b1be73fce44c76.avif?t=1748182179 width=800 height=125 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Congratulations, unfortunate soul! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're now trapped in the Sahur mansion with the most <strong>cursed zombi versions</strong> of your <strong>favorite brainrot memes</strong>. They used to make you laugh. Now they'll make you scream.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME FEATURES: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric horror with immersive sound design </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging puzzles throughout the mansion </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stealth gameplay - hide from pursuing creatures </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the story through collectible notes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easter eggs and references for meme lovers</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/1961290026f8faf8c5d4c02faaad27a9.poster.avif?t=1748182179\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/1961290026f8faf8c5d4c02faaad27a9.webm?t=1748182179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/1961290026f8faf8c5d4c02faaad27a9.mp4?t=1748182179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These monstrosities want what's left of your rotting brain, and they're not here to ask nicely. As you explore this nightmare fuel of a house you'll need to solve puzzles while avoiding becoming another creepypasta story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden throughout this dank mansion are notes from previous visitors (spoiler: they didn't make it). Read them if you dare, but more importantly, KEEP MOVING.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/0764ec664ea0bba687b9e82c31ac8f73.poster.avif?t=1748182179\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/0764ec664ea0bba687b9e82c31ac8f73.webm?t=1748182179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/0764ec664ea0bba687b9e82c31ac8f73.mp4?t=1748182179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turns out those weird animals are even worse IRL. Who knew?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve the puzzles. Dodge the memes. Touch grass (if you ever get out).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your brain is already rotting. Don't let them have the rest.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/a7660232e8fb547726f0470729fcfa89.poster.avif?t=1748182179\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/a7660232e8fb547726f0470729fcfa89.webm?t=1748182179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/a7660232e8fb547726f0470729fcfa89.mp4?t=1748182179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/90eb5cff90fa620362b1be73fce44c76.avif?t=1748182179\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras_big/90eb5cff90fa620362b1be73fce44c76.avif?t=1748182179 width=800 height=125 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Congratulations, unfortunate soul! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're now trapped in the Sahur mansion with the most <strong>cursed zombi versions</strong> of your <strong>favorite brainrot memes</strong>. They used to make you laugh. Now they'll make you scream.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME FEATURES: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric horror with immersive sound design </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging puzzles throughout the mansion </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stealth gameplay - hide from pursuing creatures </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the story through collectible notes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easter eggs and references for meme lovers</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/1961290026f8faf8c5d4c02faaad27a9.poster.avif?t=1748182179\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/1961290026f8faf8c5d4c02faaad27a9.webm?t=1748182179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/1961290026f8faf8c5d4c02faaad27a9.mp4?t=1748182179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These monstrosities want what's left of your rotting brain, and they're not here to ask nicely. As you explore this nightmare fuel of a house you'll need to solve puzzles while avoiding becoming another creepypasta story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden throughout this dank mansion are notes from previous visitors (spoiler: they didn't make it). Read them if you dare, but more importantly, KEEP MOVING.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/0764ec664ea0bba687b9e82c31ac8f73.poster.avif?t=1748182179\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/0764ec664ea0bba687b9e82c31ac8f73.webm?t=1748182179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/0764ec664ea0bba687b9e82c31ac8f73.mp4?t=1748182179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turns out those weird animals are even worse IRL. Who knew?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve the puzzles. Dodge the memes. Touch grass (if you ever get out).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your brain is already rotting. Don't let them have the rest.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/a7660232e8fb547726f0470729fcfa89.poster.avif?t=1748182179\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/a7660232e8fb547726f0470729fcfa89.webm?t=1748182179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3707660/extras/a7660232e8fb547726f0470729fcfa89.mp4?t=1748182179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
